      • Serialized Fields

        • level

          int level
          The level of the game.

        • squares

          java.util.ArrayList<Square> squares
          An ArrayList that stores all the Square objects of the Board.
          See Also:
          Square

        • state

          int state
          The state of the game.

          - State.WIN, or 1, if the player wins a level of the game

          - State.IN_PROGRESS, or 0, if the game is in progress

          - State.LOSE, or -1, if the player loses a level of the game

          See Also:
          Board.State

    • Class hoppers.Square extends javax.swing.JButton implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • squareType

          int squareType
          The type of the square

          - 1, if the type of square is GreenFrog

          - 2, if the type of square is GreenFrog2

          - 3, if the type of square is LilyPad

          - 4, if the type of square is RedFrog

          - 5, if the type of square is RedFrog2

          - 6, if the type of square is Water

        • x

          int x
          The x-axis coordinate of the Square

        • y

          int y
          The y-axis coordinate of the Square
